om-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpHdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=593089c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<blockquote>2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d527097c17c660347d6085382fb54a631e8774de","tid":1221199,"uid":246380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打可唔可以幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53626ab34776c7119c4b374891bbd100d48a650","tid":1221199,"uid":220011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"push"}]}